Maintainer: Amain (DebWrt.net) <amain@debwrt.net>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 7.0.50~)
Standards-Version: 3.8.4

Package: debwrt-hostapd
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Advanced IEEE 802.11 management daemon
 hostapd is a user space daemon for access point and authentication servers. It implements IEEE 802.11
 access point management, IEEE 802.1X/WPA/WPA2/EAP Authenticators, RADIUS client, EAP server, and 
 RADIUS authentication server. The current version supports Linux (Host AP, madwifi, Prism54 drivers)
 and FreeBSD (net80211).
 .
 This version is compiled with minimal drivers and options: nl80211 kernel driver interface and WPA
 and WEP support.
